# mpv

`*`                  - Increase volume
`/`                  - Decrease volume
`0`                  - Increase volume
`9`                  - Decrease volume
`e`                  - zoom in  (panscan)
`w`                  - zoom out (panscan)
`alt+arrow`          - Move around image
`p`                  - pause/continue
`q`                  - quit
`s`                  - screenshot
`m`                  - mute
`o`                  - show time
`i`                  - show info about played file
`ctrl+shift+<arrow>`   - go to the next/previous subtitle
`z/x`                - decrease/increase subtitle delay 
`[/]`                - increase/decrease speed of media
`{/}`                - increase/decrease speed of media exponentially



# Subtitles

## Load a subtitle file
mpv file.mp4 --sub-files=path/to/sub.srt

## Load two subtitle files to play at the same time
mpv Movie.avi --sub-file="ENG_SUBS.srt" --sub-file="RUS_SUBS.srt" --secondary-sid=2




